## 🚀 **URGENT PRIORITY TASKS**

### **1. Custom Field Builder (ACF) System - NEW FEATURE 🔥**
**Priority:** CRITICAL  
**Status:** TODO  
**Estimated Time:** 2-3 weeks  
**Type:** New Feature Development

#### **Feature Description**
Create a dynamic Custom Field Builder system similar to WordPress ACF (Advanced Custom Fields) that allows users to:
- Add custom fields to any component/page dynamically
- Choose field types (text, number, date, select, checkbox, file upload, etc.)
- Automatically render fields in the UI without manual coding
- Store field configurations in database
- Manage field groups and templates
- Export/import field configurations

#### **Technical Requirements**
```typescript
// Database Tables Needed
1. custom_fields table
   - id, name, type, label, options, validation_rules, position
2. custom_field_groups table  
   - id, name, description, location, is_active
3. custom_field_values table
   - id, field_id, entity_type, entity_id, value
4. field_templates table
   - id, name, fields_config, category
```

#### **Field Types to Support**
- Text (single line)
- Textarea (multi-line)
- Number (integer/decimal)
- Email
- URL
- Date/DateTime
- Select (dropdown)
- Multi-select
- Checkbox
- Radio buttons
- File upload
- Image upload
- Color picker
- Rich text editor
- Relationship (link to other entities)

#### **Implementation Plan**
1. **Database Design** (3 days)
   - Create custom fields tables
   - Design field configuration schema
   - Add migration scripts

2. **Backend API** (5 days)
   - Field creation/management endpoints
   - Field group management
   - Value storage/retrieval
   - Template management
   - Validation system

3. **Frontend Components** (7 days)
   - Field builder interface
   - Drag & drop field designer
   - Field renderer component
   - Template management UI
   - Field configuration modals

4. **Integration** (3 days)
   - Integrate with existing pages
   - Add field injection points
   - Test with all components
   - Documentation

#### **API Endpoints Needed**
```
POST   /custom-fields/fields          - Create field
GET    /custom-fields/fields          - List fields
PUT    /custom-fields/fields/{id}     - Update field
DELETE /custom-fields/fields/{id}     - Delete field

POST   /custom-fields/groups          - Create field group
GET    /custom-fields/groups          - List groups
PUT    /custom-fields/groups/{id}     - Update group

POST   /custom-fields/values          - Save field values
GET    /custom-fields/values          - Get field values
PUT    /custom-fields/values/{id}     - Update value

GET    /custom-fields/templates       - List templates
POST   /custom-fields/templates       - Create template
```

#### **Integration Points**
- Agent creation/editing forms
- Task forms
- User profile pages
- Settings pages
- Training lab configurations
- Marketplace items
- Dashboard widgets

